brazilians are to vote nov 15 for a successor to president jose 
sarney who cannot succeed himself the term is five years 
it will be the first direct presidential election since 1960 
when janio quadros won the military seized power in 1964 and 
relinquished it in 1985 
collor de mellos small national reconstruction party was founded 
only this year he rose in the polls from 7 percent in march to 20 
percent in april and has led since 
