changing face of television 
the 198990 networks schedule is cautious conservative and 
comfortable according to the report more shows than ever have been 
renewed there are fewer programs that might be considered 
troublesome and a heavy reliance on stars and programs that have 
worked well in the past 
the annual preview of the fall season by saatchi amp saatchi 
