simply stated blisters happen when your feet sweat and the sweat 
has nowhere to go natural fibers that absorb perspiration but dont 
move it away from your skin leave your feet moist soft and 
vulnerable to the friction you naturally get from walking or 
running and since the insides of your shoes also will be warm and 
airless youll be a walking culture medium for fungus 
several manufacturers of sports socks are using an updated 
