<TEXT>
when actress and model pamela ann martin suffered a disabling 
spinal stroke she spent a year in a hospital flat on her back but 
she still managed to get to a shopping mall on a stretcher to follow 
her passion for fashion 
i was the only person shopping for clothes from a horizontal 
position recalls the vivacious brunette who graduated from 
